---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'March 16, 2025';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Side Quests To Freedom"
  description="Privacy Policy for sidequeststofreedom.com — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonicalUrl="https://sidequeststofreedom.com/privacy-policy"
>
  <div class="bg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-1" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main class="container page-container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/links" class="breadcrumb-link">Home</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
      <span>Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <article class="prose-page">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy describes how Side Quests To Freedom ("we", "us", or "our") collects,
        uses, and shares information when you visit <strong>sidequeststofreedom.com</strong> (the "Site").
        By using the Site, you agree to the collection and use of information as described below.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We do not directly collect personal information such as your name or email address unless
        you voluntarily provide it (for example, by contacting us). However, certain third-party
        services embedded in or linked from the Site may collect data automatically when you visit.
      </p>

      <h3>Automatically Collected Data</h3>
      <p>
        Like most websites, our hosting provider and third-party services may automatically collect
        standard log data, including your IP address, browser type, referring URL, pages visited,
        and date/time of access. This data is used for security and analytics purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your browser. We use cookies in the
        following ways:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> This Site displays ads served by
          <strong>Google AdSense</strong>, which uses cookies to personalise ads based on your
          browsing activity across the web. Google may use the DoubleClick cookie to serve ads
          based on your prior visits to this and other websites.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> We may use tools such as Google Analytics to
          understand how visitors use the Site. These tools collect anonymous aggregate data
          (page views, session duration, traffic sources).
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings or opt out of
        personalised advertising via <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Ad Settings</a>.
        For more information on how Google uses data when you visit a partner site, see
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy &amp; Terms</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Links and Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        The Site contains links to external websites, including affiliate links. When you click an
        affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission. These third-party sites have
        their own privacy policies, and we have no responsibility or liability for their content or
        activities. We encourage you to review the privacy policy of any site you visit.
      </p>

      <h2>4. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>Any information collected is used to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate and maintain the Site</li>
        <li>Understand how visitors use the Site (aggregate analytics)</li>
        <li>Serve relevant advertisements via Google AdSense</li>
        <li>Respond to enquiries you send us directly</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This Site is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect
        personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal
        information, please contact us so we can delete it.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete personal
        data we hold about you, or to object to certain processing. To exercise any of these rights,
        please contact us via the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
        with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes
        your acceptance of the revised policy.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please reach out via the
        <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <SiteFooter />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.45);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb-link {
    color: rgba(var(--purple-rgb), 0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb-link:hover {
    color: var(--purple);
  }

  .prose-page h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .meta {
    font-size: 0.75rem !important;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.5) !important;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.07);
  }

  .prose-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .prose-page h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose-page p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .prose-page ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .prose-page li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .prose-page strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .prose-page a {
    color: var(--purple);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .prose-page a:hover {
    color: var(--green);
  }
</style>
